strings: <voice_0x01001CA9><se_high>Media princess: I will pray for you when you enter this cave.
<voice_0x01001CAA><se_high>Media princess: I sincerely pray I can meet you in my dreams <hero>
<voice_0x01001CAB><se_high>Media princess: I tried my best but I can't do it! I'm starting to think he's going to die too <hero>...
<voice_0x01001CAC><se_high>Media princess: You don't know how glad I am that you're okay!
<voice_0x01001CAD><se_high>Media princess: Where I can't go, don't go!
<voice_0x01001CAE><se_high>Media princess: I have a date but she looks like my sister <hero>!
<voice_0x01001CAF><se_high>Media princess: Promise me you'll never leave me!
